                | The Modern</br>
                | Evening Collection.</br>
              span.sub-heading--small
                | Custom evening wear, made-to-order.</br>
                | Because ball gowns are not meant to blend in.</br>
                <em class="link-underline">Explore</em> gowns.
        .col-md-4.col-lg-3.hidden-md.hidden-lg
          .copy-wrap.copy-align--top.extra-padding-left.text-center
            h2.heading.no-margin-md
              span.sub-heading.sub-heading--extra-large.no-margin-md.no-padding
                | The Modern Evening Collection. <br/>
                <em class="link-underline">Explore</em> gowns.


